{"tid":2068434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"粉嶺警察機動部隊基地防暴演習　警員意外受傷","createTime":"2020-06-17T16:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T17:23:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee939f9ecdcfa20733fc597b6c90bbff261b2a4d","tid":2068434,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"昨日(17日)下午約4時，一名男警員在粉嶺警察機動部隊基地進行防暴演習期間，他手及腳部意外受傷，同袍見狀隨即替治理傷勢，並召救護車送往威爾斯親王醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 東網"},{"pid":"9503e17a1daaa703bfdb24d211aab06856137c81","tid":2068434,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"我要三萬"},{"pid":"651189d052759e6e96b3de68035fa6a0a2381f06","tid":2068434,"uid":307619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"9305cd96db4f0b28b64c7f4f644e616b38c2ab77","tid":2068434,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"01f561acc964e05a145852f95c48e850e2a9aed5","tid":2068434,"uid":114792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"襲警?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd44104a701ad9ae2278867a2dece1725055e78","tid":2068434,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"即係進行緊一啲強度好高嘅訓練"},{"pid":"94710caf649c860b230ca2851024113aa76fdebc","tid":2068434,"uid":205462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHXgkFR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHXgkFR.gif&h=b28d15e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"313d8fe02098fac2a3b30d603fec6fbe5a2294ba","tid":2068434,"uid":204442,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢地會扮示威者嗌口號 聽過佢地講黑警死全家 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ed69272feb63fa1e94b78156fb430144c3affc","tid":2068434,"uid":311275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94710caf649c860b230ca2851024113aa76fdebc","tid":2068434,"uid":205462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHXgkFR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHXgkFR.gif&h=b28d15e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b011e57ec7df30831ecb4efc8045fd5a6c48ef","tid":2068434,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"死咗未"},{"pid":"df79e26bb7057c9aeda0c57d